title: LF a Duo Partner in Ranked
body:
Howdy,

I am a hardstuck Plat V support/adc main. I am looking for a duo partner to to go botlane with. Preferably an adc/bot main Plat V or higher.

Add me if interested, Kaidi (OCE). Lets see how high we can climb together.

Lets have fun on the rift. CYA{{sticker:sg-lulu}}
